<h2 id="when-to-use-content-breaks">When to use Content breaks</h2>

<p>Use Content breaks to break up a page that has differne content of information.</p>

<h2 id="when-not-to-use-a-content-break">When not to use a Content break</h2>

<p>Do not use Content breaks to break up paragraphs within a body of text or divide up forms.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-use-content-breaks">How to use Content breaks</h2>

<p>They should be used to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>thematically divide up sections of content, such as services, news and legislation</li>
  <li>show a divide between a list of clickable items, such as news articles, service links or guidance documents</li>
</ul>

